<li id="cite_note-1">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.lawfaremedia.org/article/indias-move-kashmir-unpacking-domestic-and-international-motivations-and-implications">"India's Move in Kashmir: Unpacking the Domestic and International Motivations and Implications"</a>. <i>Lawfare</i>. August 12, 2019.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Lawfare&amp;rft.atitle=India%27s+Move+in+Kashmir%3A+Unpacking+the+Domestic+and+International+Motivations+and+Implications&amp;rft.date=2019-08-12&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawfaremedia.org%2Farticle%2Findias-move-kashmir-unpacking-domestic-and-international-motivations-and-implications&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AC.+Christine+Fair" class="Z3988"></span></span>
